      "Thank you Magus. I am sure this is hard for you. Me being your former enemey. But the evil that excists now has no boundries. He was able to handle we me with ease. But believe me I will stop him."

        "Yes we will. But I'll need help. Oracal I need you to locate the spark of Dark Prime." A light flashed and  a a glowish glow shined in the distance. 

      "There he is. Lets go. He'll be no match for the two of us." The two took of towards the glow.
